refsect1.title: Description
refsect1.para: This header exposes the interface names from the Telepathy specification as cpp defines for strings, such as TP_IFACE_PROPERTIES_INTERFACE. It is automatically generated from the specification.
Since 0.7.0 it also provides cpp defines like TP_IFACE_QUARK_PROPERTIES_INTERFACE, which expand to function calls that return GQuarks for the same strings.

Since 0.9.UNRELEASED it also provides cpp defines like TP_PROP_CHANNEL_INTERFACE_GROUP_GROUP_FLAGS, which expand to string constants representing fully-qualified D-Bus property names, like org.freedesktop.Telepathy.Channel.Interface.Group.GroupFlags.
